data.c_tabDescription: Loved for its boxy cut and perfect, almost-cropped length, this is a relaxed zip-up hoodie finished with dropped shoulders and a double-layer hood. It’s made with Aritzia's Cozy Sweatfleece — premium midweight fleece famous for its soft-brushed back, sueded face and cloud-nine plush feel. The best kind of cozy. Faded Colours: Our unique wash is achieved through a special technique — instead of dyeing the fabric, we dye the finished garment for a dimensional, sun-faded look and lived-in soft feel.
data.c_tabDetails:
• Content: 78% cotton, 22% polyester; Side Panels & Ribbed Trim: 97% cotton, 3% elastane, exclusive of ornamentation
  • Care: Machine wash
  • Imported

  • Exclusive Aritzia embroidery
